## Pupil Fit Method

**Label:** pupilFitMethod

**Description:** The method employed for fitting the pupil, for example "centre-of-mass" or "ellipse". If "centre-of-mass" or "ellipse" method is used, it is RECOMMENDED to use these exact labels.
